title: President of the Republic receives Malian Foreign Minister
text: President of the Republic, Mr Abdelmadjid Tebboune, received, on Monday, the Minister of Foreign Affairs and International Cooperation of the Republic of Mali Mr Zeyni Moulaye.

The Principal Private Secretary at the Presidency of the Republic, Mr Noureddine Bardad-Daidj, Minister of Foreign Affairs, Mr Sabri Boukadoum as well as Minister of the Interior, Local Authorities and National Planning Mr Kamel Beldjoud took part in this meeting.
